  "text": "The micro-mechanical vibration gyroscope is developing with the improvement of the micro-electro-mechanical system (MEMS) technology, which results in the smaller size, lower cost, and higher performance devices. Hence, it widely used in a variety of consumer electronics applications [CITATION_1] .",
